The paper deals with the \textsc{Subset Feedback Vertex Set} problem, which is a well-studied problem in graph theory and has applications in various fields including network design and VLSI layout. The paper specifically focuses on the problem in split graphs and chordal graphs, which are both important classes of graphs in graph theory. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.DM (Discrete Mathematics), cs.CG (Computational Geometry), cs.CC (Computational Complexity), and cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory).
